<ab facs="#facs_138_line_1575444490398_130">bey vns geen lıeſʒen / das Jm nicht geen künde / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r1l29"> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> briefe wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">tün ew cʒe </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_138_line_1575444494223_135"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab></add> vviſſen / daʒ vvir dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
