<add><ab facs="#facs_138_line_1576744571720_3776">Burg<ex>er</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough"> n </del> dem </ab><ab facs="#facs_138_line_1576744573990_3781"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Beheim </ab><ab facs="#facs_138_line_1576744576780_3786"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_138_line_1576744578986_3791">müter </ab></add> noch ıht mer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_line_1575444933148_159">cʒeſprechen het / . Darvmb vvöllen vvir Jm noch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> fruntlıchs </ab>
