<ab facs="#facs_139_r5l6"><expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Andree <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> . </ab>
